      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
      *
           if        w-cnt-exe-rou-sro    =    01
                     move  02             to   v-pos
